This is a quick hotfix release to fix whatever bugs we have spotted during the final testing rounds.

### Changes

This release contains a variety of changes, including, but not limited to:

- `[*]` Fixed crashes when running winelevate
- `[*]` Fixed input not being recognized in some TUI apps on Linux
- `[*]` Fixed hardware listing errors on Linux
- `[*]` Fixed various appearance issues
- `[*]` General improvements

Review the commit history if you want to get a deep insight about the changes.

### Feedback?

If you have issues with this version, report to us by [making a new issue ticket](https://github.com/Aptivi/Nitrocid/issues/new).

